WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.670 --> 00:00:03.560
O‘sha farqlarni sanab o‘tish
bizga yaxshi boshlanish nuqtasini beradi.

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:06.370
Ulardan men qilish kerak bo‘lgan narsalar 
ro‘yxatini tuzishimm mumkin.

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:09.480
Xullas, endi bularning har 
biri orqali borasiz va

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:11.820
asta-sekin buni yakuniy 
maqsadga olib kelasiz.

00:00:13.070 --> 00:00:16.730
Biz bu birinchi bosqichdan boshlaymiz,
bu matnni kattaroq qiladi.

00:00:16.730 --> 00:00:19.420
Va bu yerda dastur
kodlashni tugatdingiz

00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:22.120
Har bir qadamda ilovani telefoningizda ishga tushirib 

00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:24.990
u haqiqiy qurilmada yaxshi ko‘rinishiga ishonch hosil.

00:00:24.990 --> 00:00:26.690
Mayli, boshlaymiz.

00:00:26.690 --> 00:00:28.160
Bu yerda atributlar ro‘yxati.

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:30.770
Atribut yoki
atributlar yonida belgi qo‘ying

00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:33.450
keyin javobingizni tekshirishga yuborib to‘g‘ri-noto‘g‘riligini ko‘ring.

00:00:33.450 --> 00:00:35.950
atributlarni to‘g‘ri tanlagandan 
so‘ng davom eting va

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:39.680
ularni o‘zgartiring, ikkala matn ko‘rinishi 
uchun matn 36sp bo‘ladigan qilib.

00:00:41.060 --> 00:00:42.890
Tugatganingizdan so‘ng,
sizning ilovangiz quyidagicha 
ko‘rinishda bo‘lishi kerak.

